:** Describes the weak gluten formation suitable for pastries.\n- **Hard Wheat Flour:** Details on the strong gluten formation, ideal for bread-making. \n\nThis detailed discussion and visual representation explain various wheat types and their purposes, providing insights into their agricultural patterns, nutritive contents, and final applications in baking and flour products."
